---

<section id="questions" class="py-12 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-yellow-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Preguntas Frecuentes -->
        <div class="mb-16">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center relative">
                    <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-500">Preguntas Frecuentes</span>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                </h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-carrusel flex md:flex-col overflow-x-auto md:overflow-visible snap-x snap-mandatory md:snap-none gap-4 md:gap-0 md:space-y-4 -mx-4 px-4 md:mx-0 md:px-0 pb-2">
                <div class="faq-item flex-shrink-0 w-[85vw] min-w-[280px] max-w-[340px] md:w-full md:min-w-0 md:max-w-none snap-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-amber-100 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center p-2 shadow-lg">
                                <img src="/assets/logo-bordart.png" alt="BordArt Logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">¿Hacen diseños personalizados?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">¡Por supuesto! Vos nos mandás tu idea y juntxs lo diseñamos para que quede perfecto.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item flex-shrink-0 w-[85vw] min-w-[280px] max-w-[340px] md:w-full md:min-w-0 md:max-w-none snap-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-amber-100 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center p-2 shadow-lg">
                                <img src="/assets/logo-bordart.png" alt="BordArt Logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">¿Puedo bordar una prenda mía?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">¡Claro que sí! Traé tu prenda y la personalizamos con el bordado que quieras.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item flex-shrink-0 w-[85vw] min-w-[280px] max-w-[340px] md:w-full md:min-w-0 md:max-w-none snap-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-amber-100 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center p-2 shadow-lg">
                                <img src="/assets/logo-bordart.png" alt="BordArt Logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">¿Se puede modificar el tamaño de los diseños?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Sí, pero solo hasta un 10% para mantener la calidad del bordado. Si necesitás un cambio mayor, lo charlamos juntxs.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item flex-shrink-0 w-[85vw] min-w-[280px] max-w-[340px] md:w-full md:min-w-0 md:max-w-none snap-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-amber-100 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center p-2 shadow-lg">
                                <img src="/assets/logo-bordart.png" alt="BordArt Logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">¿Cuántos bordados le puedo poner a una misma prenda?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">¡Todos los que se te ocurran! No hay límite, la creatividad es tuya.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item flex-shrink-0 w-[85vw] min-w-[280px] max-w-[340px] md:w-full md:min-w-0 md:max-w-none snap-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-amber-100 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center p-2 shadow-lg">
                                <img src="/assets/logo-bordart.png" alt="BordArt Logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-1">
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800 mb-2">¿Cuál es el tamaño máximo de bordado?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">El área máxima para un bordado es de 20 cm x 30 cm. Si necesitás algo más grande, consultanos.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tips de Cuidado -->
        <div class="mt-16">
            <!-- Versión mobile: acordeón -->
            <details class="md:hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-amber-50/30 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-amber-100">
                <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer select-none">
                    <div class="text-center w-full">
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold relative inline-block">
                            <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-500">Tips de Cuidado</span>
                            <div class="absolute -bottom-1 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-16 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    <span class="ml-2 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-200 accordion-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2">
                    <p class="text-base text-gray-700 text-center mb-4 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                        Para que tus prendas siempre tengan ese color intenso y ese bordado siga dándole brillo a tu ropa, te recomendamos:
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">Lavar las prendas oscuras del revés y con agua fría o templada preferentemente</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">No dejar secar los oscuros al rayo del sol</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">No planchar directamente sobre el bordado</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">No colocar los pines en el lavarropa</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </details>

            <!-- Versión desktop: igual que antes -->
            <div class="hidden md:block">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-12">
                    <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center relative">
                        <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-500">Tips de Cuidado</span>
                        <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 to-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
                    </h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-amber-50/30 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-amber-100 p-8 md:p-10">
                    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 text-center mb-8 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                        Para que tus prendas siempre tengan ese color intenso y ese bordado siga dándole brillo a tu ropa, te recomendamos:
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Lavar las prendas oscuras del revés y con agua fría o templada preferentemente</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-amber-500 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">No dejar secar los oscuros al rayo del sol</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-amber-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">No planchar directamente sobre el bordado</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="tip-item flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-400 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">No colocar los pines en el lavarropa</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Carrusel móvil Preguntas Frecuentes: ocultar scrollbar */
    @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .faq-carrusel {
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
        }
        .faq-carrusel::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
    }
</style>
